Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.08,0:00:07.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ヤバーい　何なの　この量
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,協力しても終わる気がしない…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:15.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,宿題　噂どおり鬼畜だったな　うちの学校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:20.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,さっさと終わらせて　受験勉強の方やりたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:26.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やっぱりえっちゃんみたいに予備校もう始めとくべきかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦はどうすんの
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,冬あたりからかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.77,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,うちお金ないしなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.16,0:00:36.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺　宿題終わったら先生にコクるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃ…じゃあ　私も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.45,0:00:50.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おお　マジ？　同時に行くか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:54.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,結局　ノリと勢い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,背高い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの　お兄さん　すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:42.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,カットモデルとか興味ないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,タダ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.02,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい　カットだけなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その頭　暑くないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,切っちゃいましょうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大丈夫　あんまり切りたくないから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すみません
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いえいえ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,篤也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう　捜した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お似合いカップル…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,悪い　この辺慣れてなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,方向音痴だもんね　篤也は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,わざわざ隣町の夏期講習受けに来なくてもいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗がいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,目合っちゃった　ヤバッ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,相変わらず長ったらしい髪　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,切れば？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗はさらに綺麗になった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:47.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,親戚の葬式で　６年ぶりに早苗と再会した
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,クラスの女子とは全然違った
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:56.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,きょうだいも友達もあまりいない俺の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,たった一人のいとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,桐嶋篤也？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,目がこっちを見てる…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,で…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でっかっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんた　こんなだったじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,育ったね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お…覚えてた
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗も　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大人っぽくなった　すごく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,変わってないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,綺麗だ　付き合って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗の嫌そうな顔ったらなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,回想　終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗はさらに綺麗になった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.10,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,女優さんにでもなるの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　大学生になりたいんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺はしつこい　
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,諦めない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗に好きな人がいることを知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,別にいい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,高校で好きなやつできたって話でしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,別にいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それだからってわけじゃないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そいつとうまくいきそうにないみたいだし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それは最近の早苗見てれば分かるし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:32.40,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺は体のいい相談役　血のつながった男友達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:36.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　早苗のこと何でも知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,女の子だから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かってよ　篤也のことを好きにはなれない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗は…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,女だからその人が好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:55.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,女だからその人とうまくいかないの
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺　複雑なこと分かんないから　無神経かも
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:05.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:10.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　早苗が誰かを好きになったのは初めてだし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何かうれしいし
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,早苗が好きなやつなら　俺も好き
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,変？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.76,0:06:24.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　私　たぶん男は嫌い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺のことは嫌いじゃないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:34.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ってことは　桐嶋篤也って一人の人間として見てるってことで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　性別なんて関係ないってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:44.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　性別なんてカテゴリをつけたくない　篤也には
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その子にはカテゴリをつけてるから好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　俺も可能性ゼロじゃないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,目合っちゃう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.32,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,勉強？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やったやった　
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.40,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一応ね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,２人とも真面目だもん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,優等生なの　私たち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,怖い？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そりゃあ…すげえ怖い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,返事聞きたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,駄目って分かってるけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あいつだと思っていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.80,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あれ　こんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:43.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,変なのいまさら　わざわざ言うって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もともと麦と私はそれありきで
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か　俺だけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ならいいけど　別に
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ちょっ　なになに　分かんない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,言ってよ　言ってくれなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もしかしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.64,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,同じかもしれないし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か　いつからとか分かんねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,代わりにできない　花火のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それって　つまり　あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あれ　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か…言葉出ない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何で　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:27.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっと　早く何か言わなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まっ　いっか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お互い覚悟決めたんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なるようにしかなんねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.88,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そのとき　私もはっきりと　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もうすっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦にお兄ちゃんを重ねて見ることはなくなっていたことに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,気付いてしまったのでした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ここまででいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ありがとう　送ってくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,夏は短い
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:42.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,時間は巻き戻らない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,眼鏡掛け始めたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,似合ってるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,先生って感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,教員試験　おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃんも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.18,0:10:36.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私のは別にただの高校受験だし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　そこ結構難関だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:43.12,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんは夢をかなえたんだもん　すごいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ホントにおめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.84,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やだ　泣いてんの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:55.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　花ちゃんもおっきくなったなって　ふと…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう　すぐ子ども扱いする…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,な…に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,覚えてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃんが雪の日に迷子になって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,帰り道　手を引いて歩いた
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もうそんな昔のこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いいじゃん　今日だけ　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,家まで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,キラキラした思い出たち
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どれもささいなことばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:33.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ずっと大切にしてきた　私の宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:39.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その中のどれか一つでも　あなたが覚えていてくれたら
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大げさじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は生きていけると思った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.92,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなた以上の人なんて　どこにもいないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いびつでも　不器用でも
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,全力で恋した
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう逃げない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,宿題　終わったね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:37.20,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦はあしたの昼　私は夜に告白する
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,失恋じゃなくて？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,悪い悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まっ　でもいいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,１人より　２人一緒ならさ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,よし　あしたの22時にここで待ち合わせな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何だか　麦の顔真っすぐ見れないや
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何でよ　いまさら
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃ　あしたな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.25,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,やだ　やだやだ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何これ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,顔熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おやすみ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何なの…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:30.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,励ましてくれたのかな　麦なりに
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:31.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:35.17,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ドキドキで震え消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦にドキドキって変なの
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも　嫌じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.42,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,手をつないでる夢を見た
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰だったんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:12.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.32,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,どうしたの　あっついね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すいません　わざわざ呼び出して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:24.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ううん　カワイイ教え子のためですから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あと麦ちゃんは特別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,進路の悩み相談かな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:34.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今から俺　この人に振られるんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:39.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,相変わらず崩さないね　その仮面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:41.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あの…　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,えっとですね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.66,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,立ち話？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,先生喉渇いちゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,喫茶店でも行こうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,完全にあっちのペース
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,麦ちゃん日焼けした？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ヤベえ　うれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.49,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,マジで焼けないの気にしてたんで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう嫌みだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:16.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,色白で色素薄い感じ　うらやましいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.72,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いや　俺のは色白通り越して土気色ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,死んでますから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.29,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,女の子はそういう方が好きだと思うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,先生は？　アイドル系がいいの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.30,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それともバリバリ男らしい系？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.94,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,綺麗系が好きでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.85,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,まあ　ハゲ親父とも寝てたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,好き
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:15:59.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でした
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.97,0:16:01.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.46,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知ってるのを知ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それは知らなかったなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.58,0:16:09.74,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,嘘つきですね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私は麦ちゃんのこと　好きよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.28,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,浮かれんな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたは嘘ばかりついてる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.05,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.05,0:16:22.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ある
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,知ってる　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.48,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ずっと見てきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おい　駄目だって
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,引けよ　もう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,踏み込むな　俺のバカ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.41,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,その人は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから好きだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,手に入らないから　好きだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　今…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:54.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　あなたは絶対　俺のことなんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,目の前にいるこの人は？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺を…見てる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,嘘じゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.98,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,私もずっと麦ちゃんのこと…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,決めたのに　俺　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.89,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう一人にしないって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,言っときますけど　俺知ってます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.08,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:26.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたが　どうしようもなく男好きの性悪で
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:29.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,自己愛こじらせたクソ女だってことを
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰のことも好きにならないくせに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.13,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰からも好かれないと気が済まない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.97,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺の…俺の好意だって　別に
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:41.56,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,誰でもいい　俺じゃなくったって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.70,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,カワイイ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:48.00,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　どうしてついてきちゃったの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はい　もうこれは俺が悪かったって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:57.26,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,村人レベル１がラスボスに挑むようなもんでした
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:17:58.90,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,認めます
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.24,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,「好き」なんて　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,絶対信じない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,絶対的戦力差
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.44,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そんなぺらっぺらの紙切れみたいな「好き」に価値なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,でも…　
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.60,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,だから　俺がここにいるのは…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.78,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたの…初めてになりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:23.01,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,俺が　あなたを変えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.16,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,おーい　安楽岡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,夏休みの宿題　終わってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,はーい　先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,何か顔見るの久しぶりだね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:44.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そう　夏休みって　先生に会えなくなるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.65,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あのさ　お兄ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.21,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大事な話って何か分かる？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,なん…だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.04,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,全然分かんない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.62,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんのそういうとこ　好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,もう　バカにして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,好きでした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,過去形？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.68,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.61,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今も好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.93,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,それが大事な話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,いつから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今まで散々鈍かったくせして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:27.76,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,すぐ気が付いて真面目になってくれるとこ　好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:33.06,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,ずっと…ずっとずっと前から
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:37.57,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,相手の気持ちにシンクロして考えちゃうとこ　好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.86,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,言葉にしたら　どんどんあふれて…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,声が好き　顔が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.58,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,しぐさが好き　話し方が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.81,0:19:52.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,考えてることが好き　優しいとこが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.36,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一番大切なとき　そうやって受け止めてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:59.22,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あなたが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.14,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.96,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あ…あの　分かってるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:12.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,震えてるのは　ちゃんと私じゃないこと分かってるからで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,あんなふうに泣いたのはいつぶりだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:25.18,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,お兄ちゃんが強く強く抱き締めてくれると
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.45,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,これが最初で最後って実感して　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:29.73,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,また泣けて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,全身で一つもこぼさないように　私も受け止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.33,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大切にされてること　うれしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.82,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,たとえ恋じゃなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:45.53,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,そして私の長かった片思いは…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.09,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,花ちゃん　ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.52,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.54,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,今度こそ前に進むの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.50,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,きっとできる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.34,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,きっと変われる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.69,TEXT JP - A-OTF Ryumin Pro EH-KL,,0,0,0,,一人じゃ…ないから
Comment: 0,0:00:00.93,0:00:00.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,----------TEXT_CN----------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:04.08,0:00:07.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,要命了 怎么这么多
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.80,0:00:10.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就算有人帮忙也做不完…
Dialogue: 1,0:00:10.84,0:00:15.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们学校的作业 果真不是给人做的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.88,0:00:20.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好想赶紧做完 开始备战高考啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.88,0:00:26.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我是不是应该像小绘那样去上冲刺班呢
Dialogue: 1,0:00:26.49,0:00:28.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,麦 你要怎么办
Dialogue: 1,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,到了冬天再说
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.17,0:00:34.77,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们家没钱啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.16,0:00:36.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我做完作业后 就去向她表白
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.26,0:00:47.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那…那我也去
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.45,0:00:50.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真的吗 要一起行动啊
Dialogue: 1,0:00:51.04,0:00:54.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,全靠一时的冲动
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好高啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.54,0:02:39.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这位小哥 打扰一下
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.78,0:02:42.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,请问你有兴趣做发模吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,免费？
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.02,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是的 单理发的话
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你顶着这头发不热吗
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.88,0:02:52.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还是剪掉算了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.98,0:02:56.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不用了 我不是很想剪
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.88,0:02:59.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.22,0:03:01.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,笃也
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.77,0:03:04.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,让我好找啊
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.14,0:03:06.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好般配的一对…
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.18,0:03:17.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我对这边不太熟
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.56,0:03:20.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,笃也就是个路痴嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.10,0:03:24.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,何必特意跑到邻市来参加暑期补习呢
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.96,0:03:26.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为有你在
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.09,0:03:31.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对视了 不好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你头发还是那么长
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.17,0:03:36.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,去剪了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.18,0:03:40.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗变得更漂亮了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.65,0:03:47.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,时隔六年 我在亲戚的葬礼上又遇到了早苗
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她和我班上的女生完全不同
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.57,0:03:56.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我没有兄弟姐妹 也没什么朋友
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.74,0:03:58.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她是我唯一的表亲
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,桐岛笃也？
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.12,0:04:08.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她在看我…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好高
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你原来不是才到这吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.36,0:04:16.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,长大了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.10,0:04:19.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她…还记得我
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.26,0:04:21.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗也是
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,变得比以前成熟多了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我没怎么变啦
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.06,0:04:32.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你好漂亮 做我女朋友吧
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.58,0:04:39.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗一脸无比嫌弃的样子
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,回忆结束
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,早苗变得更漂亮了
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.10,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你想当演员吗
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.08,0:04:55.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不 我只想上大学而已
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.94,0:05:00.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我纠缠不休
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,绝不放手
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.72,0:05:05.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就算明知道她有喜欢的人
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.32,0:05:07.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不就是你在高中有了喜欢的人吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.85,0:05:13.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.26,0:05:15.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.45,0:05:17.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你别误会 我没别的意思
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.01,0:05:21.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,只是觉得你们似乎遇到了阻碍
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,看你最近的样子就知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:05:27.36,0:05:32.40,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我是她的知心哥哥 也是血脉相连的男闺蜜
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.92,0:05:36.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以 我想了解她的一切
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为她…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是个女生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,醒醒吧 我是不可能喜欢上你的
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.46,0:05:48.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你喜欢她…
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.52,0:05:51.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是因为她是女生吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.02,0:05:55.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为她是女生才有阻碍吗
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.86,0:05:59.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,太复杂的事情我不懂 我有点缺心眼
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.98,0:06:05.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不会说话…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.61,0:06:10.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过 这是你第一次喜欢上别人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我替你高兴
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,既然你喜欢她 那我也喜欢
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,奇怪吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.76,0:06:24.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过 我可能讨厌男性
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但你并不讨厌我啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.06,0:06:34.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,由此可见 我桐岛笃也在你眼中只是一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.42,0:06:38.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以说 爱情和性别无关
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.32,0:06:44.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以说 我不想给你贴上性别的标签啊
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那你喜欢她是因为给她贴标签了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那么 我也不是完全没有可能嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,差点对视
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.29,0:07:02.32,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,学习？
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.96,0:07:04.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,学了学了
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.21,0:07:06.40,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还是要学的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.74,0:07:09.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,毕竟我们都很认真
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都是好学生
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你怕吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,当然…非常怕
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.78,0:07:27.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我怕听到她的回答
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.66,0:07:29.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,虽然我知道肯定没戏
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你可以把我想象成她
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.60,0:07:39.80,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,咦 突然觉得…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.34,0:07:43.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在刻意说这话有点奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.21,0:07:47.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们本来就是这样相处的
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.62,0:07:50.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,只有我这样吗
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.74,0:07:56.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其实这样也好
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,等等 什么意思 我不懂
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说嘛 你不说我怎么会懂
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,或许…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.64,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我和你一样
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不知道从什么时候开始
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.89,0:08:15.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我再也无法拿你当替身了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.84,0:08:18.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也就是说 那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.48,0:08:20.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么…词穷了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.25,0:08:23.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.14,0:08:27.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说点什么 快说点什么啊
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.12,0:08:31.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不想这些了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,反正我们都决定好了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.76,0:08:36.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也只能走一步算一步了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.88,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,当时 我也清楚地意识到
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我已经
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.82,0:08:54.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不再把麦当做哥哥的替身来看待了
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不再透过他去看哥哥了
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.52,0:09:01.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,到这里就好
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢你送我回来
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,夏天很短暂
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.61,0:09:42.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,时间一去不复返
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.28,0:10:19.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.13,0:10:24.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你戴眼镜了啊
Dialogue: 1,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不知道合不合适
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,很有老师的派头
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.97,0:10:31.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,恭喜你通过教师资格考试
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.78,0:10:32.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也恭喜你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.18,0:10:36.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我只不过考上了高中而已
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.72,0:10:39.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那所学校很难考的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.68,0:10:43.12,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哥哥你才厉害呢 实现了自己的梦想
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.56,0:10:44.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我衷心祝贺你
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.08,0:10:50.84,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别啊 你在哭吗
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.84,0:10:55.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没有 我只是一想到小花也长大了 就忍不住…
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.46,0:10:57.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真是的 总把我当小孩子…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.01,0:11:01.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,做…什么
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.04,0:11:03.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那次小花你在雪天里迷路了
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们是牵着手走回去的
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.26,0:11:12.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都多少年前的事了…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,来嘛 就今天
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,牵手走回家
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.94,0:11:18.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好难为情
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,每段灿烂的回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.42,0:11:28.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,都是琐碎的小事
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.02,0:11:33.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是我一直珍藏的宝物
Dialogue: 1,0:11:34.84,0:11:39.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,只要你能将这其中任何一件事记在心里
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.37,0:11:41.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,毫不夸张地说
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.34,0:11:44.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那便足以支撑我活下去
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.65,0:11:50.92,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这世上谁都不及你好
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,扭曲也好 笨拙也罢
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.29,0:12:10.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我已拼命爱过
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.54,0:12:22.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我不会再逃避
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,终于做完作业了
Dialogue: 1,0:12:32.13,0:12:37.20,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,明天你在白天表白 我在晚上表白
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不是失恋吗
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.42,0:12:41.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.77,0:12:44.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过 这样也不赖
Dialogue: 1,0:12:44.86,0:12:47.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,两个人一起失恋 总好过一个人
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.25,0:12:49.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说定了 明晚十点就在这里碰面
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.58,0:13:01.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,突然有点不敢看麦的脸
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.10,0:13:04.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么啊 都什么时候了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那明天见
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.25,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有没有搞错
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,干嘛这样
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,脸好烫
Dialogue: 1,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么回事…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.22,0:13:30.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,难道那是麦给我的鼓励吗
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.16,0:13:31.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.01,0:13:35.17,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,心跳得太快 反倒不发抖了
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真奇怪 我居然为他心跳加速
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其实 这感觉还不错
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.42,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我在梦里和别人牵着手
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那人是谁呢
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.69,0:14:12.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小麦
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.37,0:14:16.32,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有什么事呀 大热天的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.42,0:14:20.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 麻烦你跑一趟
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.72,0:14:24.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没关系 都是为了我可爱的学生嘛
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,再说 小麦是特别的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是要谈升学的烦恼吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.61,0:14:34.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我马上就要被这个人拒绝了吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.84,0:14:39.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她的伪装还是那么完美
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.04,0:14:41.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.58,0:14:43.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.30,0:14:45.66,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,站着说吗
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,老师口渴了
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.46,0:14:52.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,去咖啡厅聊吧
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,局面完全被她掌控了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.56,0:15:02.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小麦晒黑了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.20,0:15:04.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.38,0:15:05.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真的假的 好开心
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.14,0:15:08.49,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还为晒不黑这事发愁来着
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,得了便宜还卖乖
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.04,0:15:16.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你的皮肤白皙透亮 让我好生羡慕呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.72,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哪有 我的肤色已经算是灰白了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.72,0:15:20.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一点活力都没有
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.29,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我觉得女生反而喜欢你这样的
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.72,0:15:29.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,老师你喜欢的是奶油小生
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.30,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,还是干练的男子汉呢
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.62,0:15:33.94,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,应该喜欢花美男吧
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.85,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过 她也睡过秃头大叔
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.36,0:15:50.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.13,0:15:59.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,曾经喜欢过
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.97,0:16:01.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.17,0:16:04.46,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道你知道
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.94,0:16:07.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这我就不知道了
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.58,0:16:09.74,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你真会说谎
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.85,0:16:14.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我还挺喜欢你的哦
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.28,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,别窃喜
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你总是满口谎言
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.05,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我才没有…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.05,0:16:22.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,有的
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.48,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为我一直在关注你
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.89,0:16:28.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂 不能这样
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.13,0:16:31.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,快收手吧
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.25,0:16:34.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 别陷进去
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.33,0:16:36.41,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她是…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.14,0:16:43.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以我才喜欢她
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.85,0:16:47.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,越是得不到 就越发喜欢
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那现在…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.08,0:16:54.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以 你是绝对不会喜欢我的…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,眼前的人会喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 1,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,她在…看着我
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.37,0:17:02.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我没有说谎
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.26,0:17:05.98,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也一直很喜欢麦…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.74,0:17:09.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我明明已经决定
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.89,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,不再让她孤独一人
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,丑话说在前面 我知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.08,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,知道什么
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.08,0:17:26.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你坏到骨子里 没有男人就活不下去
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.66,0:17:29.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是个自恋成瘾的妖艳贱货
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,自己不会喜欢上别人
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.13,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,却容不得别人不喜欢自己
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.50,0:17:37.97,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…我的好感 你也不稀罕
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.58,0:17:41.56,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对你来说谁都可以 不是我也无所谓…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.66,0:17:43.70,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.38,0:17:48.00,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要跟我来这里呢
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是 都怪我不自量力
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.84,0:17:57.26,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就好比Lv.1的村民来挑战终极大Boss一样
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.90,0:17:58.90,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我承认
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.24,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你说喜欢我
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我绝对不信
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.48,0:18:05.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,双方实力相差悬殊
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.69,0:18:06.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.90,0:18:10.44,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,像纸片一样轻飘单薄的「喜欢」二字毫无价值
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.98,0:18:14.60,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我之所以还跟来 只是因为…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.78,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我想成为…你第一个喜欢的人
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.86,0:18:23.01,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我要改变你
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.16,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喂 安乐冈
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.92,0:18:32.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,暑假作业写完了吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.64,0:18:35.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,写完啦 老师
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.29,0:18:39.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,感觉好久没有见到你了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.28,0:18:44.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是啊 暑假期间就见不到老师了
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.60,0:18:48.65,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,对了 哥哥
Dialogue: 1,0:18:49.08,0:18:51.21,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,你知道我有什么要紧事吗
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,是…什么呢
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.60,0:18:57.04,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,完全猜不到
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.80,0:19:01.62,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我就喜欢哥哥的这一点
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.77,0:19:03.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,又拿我寻开心
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.37,0:19:05.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我喜欢过你
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么是过去时
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.90,0:19:07.68,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.37,0:19:09.61,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在也喜欢
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.93,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这就是我说的要紧事
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.54,0:19:19.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,从什么时候开始的
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.49,0:19:23.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喜欢你之前还迟钝得要命
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.98,0:19:27.76,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一旦反应过来 就立刻认真对待
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.60,0:19:33.06,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,从很久…很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.98,0:19:37.57,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喜欢你总是将心比心 为他人着想
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.86,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,说了喜欢你 就一发不可收拾…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.90,0:19:45.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喜欢你的声音 喜欢你的脸庞
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.58,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喜欢你的举止 喜欢你的言谈
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.81,0:19:52.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,喜欢你的思想 喜欢你的温柔
Dialogue: 1,0:19:53.04,0:19:57.36,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,更喜欢你 在最重要的时刻能像这样
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.94,0:19:59.22,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,给我依靠
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.29,0:20:02.14,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.14,0:20:06.96,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,其…其实 我知道的
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.96,0:20:12.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我在颤抖 是因为我知道你喜欢的人不是我
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.69,0:20:20.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我有多久没这样哭过了呢
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.04,0:20:25.18,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,当哥哥紧紧抱住我的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.45,0:20:28.45,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我明白这是第一次也是最后一次
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.61,0:20:29.73,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哭得更伤心了
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.45,0:20:34.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我沉浸在拥抱中 不想错过一丝一毫
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.17,0:20:38.33,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,他这么珍惜我 我很高兴
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.92,0:20:40.82,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,哪怕他不是出于爱
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.24,0:20:45.53,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,就这样 我漫长的单恋…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.86,0:20:49.09,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,小花 谢谢你
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.52,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.25,0:21:00.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,我不怕
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.54,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,这次总算可以前进了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.32,0:21:09.50,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一定可以的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.02,0:21:12.34,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,一定可以改变的
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.50,0:21:18.69,TEXT CN - 方正小标宋_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为我…不是孤独一人
